To(Object[].class);\n        assertThat(SampleTableFunction.constructorCalls).isEqualTo(1);\n        assertThat(SampleTableFunction.lastName).isEqualTo(\"active\");\n        assertThat(SampleTableFunction.lastMinimumId).isEqualTo(7);\n    }\n\n    public static final class SampleTableFunction {\n\n        private static int constructorCalls;\n        private static String lastName;\n        private static int lastMinimumId;\n\n        public SampleTableFunction() {\n            constructorCalls++;\n        }\n\n        public SampleScannableTable eval(String name, int minimumId) {\n            lastName = name;\n            lastMinimumId = minimumId;\n            return new SampleScannableTable();\n        }\n\n        private static void resetInvocationState() {\n            constructorCalls = 0;\n            lastName = null;\n            lastMinimumId = 0;\n        }\n    }\n\n    public static final class SampleScannableTable extends AbstractTable implements ScannableTable {\n\n        @Override\n        public RelDataType getRowType(RelDataTypeFactory typeFactory) {\n            return typeFactory.builder()\n                    .add(\"ID\", SqlTypeName.INTEGER)\n                    .add(\"NAME\", SqlTypeName.VARCHAR)\n                    .build();\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public Enumerable<Object[]> scan(DataContext root) {\n            return Linq4j.emptyEnumerable();\n        }\n    }\n}\n"}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1833, "output": 856, "cacheRead": 33280, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 35969, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1780833987206, "responseId": "resp_0812bd3afd74c931016a255ec3b88881938dd31e7d1f73e068"}, "toolResults": [{"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_mWtd2r4g9pXRnF5Th0PflDPS|fc_0812bd3afd74c931016a255ec94a5481939d9ff968923e09cb", "toolName": "write", "content": [{"type": "t